comments: Hunter (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position on DeRozan (CHI) during the drive.
DeRozan (CHI) gathers the ball against his side and takes more than two steps after gathering.
Huerter (ATL) legally contests White's (CHI) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Huerter (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dosunmu (CHI) and absorbs the contact.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hunter (ATL) and initiates marginal contact as he goes around the screen.
Hunter (ATL) gives DeRozan (CHI) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (ATL).
Replay review of the foul called on DeRozan (CHI) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  DeRozan makes contact to Huerter's (ATL) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Jones Jr. (CHI) makes marginal contact with Hunter's (ATL) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his shot near the rim.
